description:
This is a 31 minute workout called '30 Minutes Workout - Virtual Scenery - Treadmill / Exercise Machine (Cotswolds UK) 1080/60fps' from the channel Rickvanman - Variety Channel.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill and Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Mindful Walk and The Explorer's Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

Original workout description: Treadmill? Exercise bike? Cross trainer? Rowing machine? Flying carpet? Beat the boredom with a virtual tour around the picturesque Hobbit Shires of Gloucester and the Cotswolds, while you work out for a full 30 minutes.  SEE NOTES BELOW REGARDING SPEED...
The music was made by me and I acknowledge not to everyone's tastes, so do feel free to mute and use your own music :o)
(Best enjoyed at full 1080p @ 60 frames per second)

SPEED NOTES:  I've had some feedback comments regarding the speed of the video not being "realistic" and not accurately representing running or walking. Before publishing, I experimented creating the video at various jogging or cycling speeds, but found with the slower speeds, the visuals got tedious very quickly.
